{"type": "article", "id": 15170, "title": "“生锈”的眼镜架", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-21T07:39:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071224439L0uaPwVMeU3ncEB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t向来崇尚自然的波特兰制镜品牌 Shwood 推出了一款“生锈”的眼镜架，在镜框的一侧嵌入了经过特殊氧化的黄铜，让蓝色、金色和绿色自然地组合在一起，以创造出非常特别的漩涡型纹路。这样的设计像是在向时尚挑战。有木框和醋酸纤维两种，<a href=\"http://www.shwoodshop.com/us/collections/oxidized\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142434fNl5WRuSynbmJZ6X.jpg\" width=\"570\" height=\"342\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142435iMaJg6bCtclVsNU0.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614243512fWAB7Ecbv5rLUp.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142436iFL7uTckvaz85bgB.jpg\" width=\"570\" height=\"342\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}